---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken & Baked Rice with Sweetcorn & Sour Cream
description: Fresh, colourful and bursting with flavour, our Tex-Mex chicken recipe is about to become a weeknight favourite. Tomato paste adds a beautiful richness to the oven-baked rice, while the spices get to work on the succulent chicken strips that are seared to golden perfection.
